ity</a> - D-Wave System's Leap Community Forum.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-04T08:33:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"desireevl/awesome-quantum-computing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://discuss.pennylane.ai/\">Pennylane Discussion Forum</a> - Discussion forum for quantum machine learning, both using simulations and on near term hardware.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-04T08:33:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"desireevl/awesome-quantum-computing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://u.strawberryfields.ai/slack\">Strawberry Fields Community</a> - Slack channel for Xanadu and Strawberry Fields photonic/CV quantum computing discussions.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-04T08:33:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DavidLambauer/awesome-magento2","categoryHTML":"<h2>Open Source Extensions</h2><h3>Development Utilities</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gwillem/magevulndb\">MageVulnDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gwillem/magevulndb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">153</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":153,\"repo\":\"gwillem/magevulndb\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Central repository for third party Magento extensions with known security issues.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-04T07:47:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"Zheaoli/awesome-coins","categoryHTML":"<h2>☤ Reading Material</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.binance.vision\">Binance Academy</a> — Open access education provided b